summary:
I have moved back to the United States. I have entered the restaurant industry as I see that a better fit for me with my hard work as my masters degree in IT cybersecurity, being fluent in Russian, and IT knowledge has not gotten me far nor has anyone seen my background as an asset. However, I am proud to have the 8+ years of experience in help desk, cyber security, service desk, and deskside technician support where i can provide further growth, safety, and success for any organization i am with. 
I speak fluent English, Russian and Spanish. 
 
Skilled in:
Data Privacy, VMWare, Airwatch, IT Chat, ID Manager, Microsoft Intune Company Portal mobile management, Intune Azure Portal, Mobile Device Management, Windows OS, MAC OS, Network Security Implementation, Azure portal, SAP, SAP Fieldglass, Peoplesoft, Maximo, DAE, Barracuda, Service Now (SNOW), Ivanti Cloud Management ITSM, Ivanti Neurons, AD Manager Plus, OKTA, SSO, AWS, Ivanti Management Console, MS SQL, UIS, TSO, BATEST, EDI, JIRA, NICE phone system, Connect Wise, Citrix Workspace Cloud, XenDesktop, XenApp, SpeedTest (beta.speedtest.net), Mitel Connect phone system, NICE phone system, VPNs, Cisco, Pulse Secure, Global Protect, RSA, Logic Monitor, Powershell, VMs, decommissioning printers, IT service desk, servers, print servers, Microsoft 365, Active Directory, remote assist clients, LogMeIn agent, Team Viewer, RDP, VNC, MSRA, ITSM, NSE1, NSE2, NSE3 certifications, FortiSIEM, Fortinet products, Fortinet Security, FortiGuard, FortiGate, hard drives, solid state drives, quality and assurance testing of VR virtual reality software, AR augmented reality software, music production software and engineering, FLstudio, native instruments, Mixed reality apps. 

Project Skills: 
Detail-oriented, organized, analytical, dedicated, self-motivated, strong sense of honesty and integrity.
Communication Skills: 
Interpersonal communication, targeted, though, fluent in Russian 
Computer Applications: 
Sales Force, Adobe Professional, All Microsoft business applications, competency in Microsoft Office and Operating Systems, all Windows operating systems, all Apple iOS devices, all MacOS laptops and computers, all mobile devices, SharePoint, Oracle, cyber security investigation, detection, and analysis, virus cleans & tune-up optimizations using tech drives on all Windows computers and laptops, and use all the necessary tools and software to update, understanding of network design, computer security, firewalls, hard drive analyses, custom built computers for customers, rebuilt computers for specific diagnoses.
